  <brief_title>Study of Sequential Administration of Oral 6-Thioguanine After Methotrexate in Patients With LCH</brief_title>
  <official_title>Study of Sequential Administration of Oral 6-Thioguanine After Methotrexate in Patients With Langerhans Cell in Histiocytosis (LCH)</official_title>
